<span id="docs-internal-guid-d8ac59c4-ef65-afec-8381-9ba02282ee2f"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">John Gold Group</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;is a company engaged in airline ticketing and cargo forwarding services. It’s been in the business since 1996 which has started from a single ticketing outlet known as&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">John Gold Travel &amp; Tour Services</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. It has grown in the industry through its high quality standards of services to its customers and clients. We are now leading the airline ticketing services with its continuous effort to widen the scope of market here and abroad. Tying up with huge companies in providing technologies in ticketing system and business model in which </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Biyahe.com.ph</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> was created.</span></span>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
                                                    <div><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></span></div><div><span id="docs-internal-guid-d8ac59c4-ef65-f7e3-f992-99c83ab67a3e"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">In year 2000, the company joined the cargo forwarding business,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">John Gold Cargo Forwarder</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">, to provide the fastest, most efficient and cost effective logistics solutions to its clients. Because we are the top agent of &nbsp;major airlines, it has now expanded to various major cities nationwide along with its home base in Davao. With the opportunity seen in magnifying the services, John Gold has opened another business branded as </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Cargo King</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> to serve the door-to-door needs of its clients.</span></span><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></span></div><div><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></span></div><div><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></span></div><div><br></div><div><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></span></div><div><span id="docs-internal-guid-d8ac59c4-ef66-1dae-e070-5ab3ef3d898e"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">VISION</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">To be the trailblazer in innovating system and service technology in terms of travel and tours and logistics. </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">MISSION</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Family Oriented</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We promote a family oriented culture which makes our workforce the asset of the company thus customer care is second nature.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Efficiency</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We invest in training our employees in order to equip them with quality customer service and expertise on our products.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Innovative</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We create advance service technologies for travel and logistics to be consistent to clientele at anytime.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Visibility</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Expansion is our key to make our presence felt everywhere thus make it a goal to promote our brand nationwide.</span></p><div><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-d8ac59c4-ef66-6f9c-66dc-62eb8fa8bc4a"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline;">CORE VALUES</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;">These are the qualities that would keep us one. &nbsp;Wherever we are and we go, we always carry this as part of our discipline. We perceive these core values as factors that will contribute to employees’ &nbsp;growth and development.</span></p><div><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;">         <b>HUMILITY</b></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><b>         INTEGRITY</b></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><b>         DRIVE FOR EXCELLENCE</b></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><b>         OUTSTANDING SERVICES</b></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><b><br></b></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-d8ac59c4-ef67-cd54-bdbb-086fa6e24e6f"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline; vertical-align: baseline;">Humility</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;">This is a virtue that involves treating others equality, sharing what you know, being submissive and respectful to others. &nbsp;It also means that we seek first to understand others than being understood, thus, we intently listen, we sincerely empathize and we show genuine care.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline; vertical-align: baseline;">Integrity</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;">When there’s honesty, trust would always surround. &nbsp;We do right things even there’s no one is watching. &nbsp;We believe we can also earn respect from others out of this.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline;"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline;">Drive of Excellence</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;">We commit our every effort not just to meet the requirements but to go the extra mile. &nbsp;We give our best without expecting anything in return.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; text-decoration-line: underline; vertical-align: baseline;">Outstanding Service</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;">We believe that in order to stay in the business, we aim no room for complaints. &nbsp;We extend service that is beyond expectation. &nbsp;We also believe that outstanding service begins at home. &nbsp;We make sure that our employees receive the same treatment that we ought to do with our external customers because they are our first customers.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;"><br></span></p></span></span></div></span></span></div></span></div>